  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For the polynomial function <math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi>\n</math>, the graph of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"y equals f left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math> in the <em>xy</em>-plane passes through the points <math alttext=\"left parenthesis negative 5 comma 0 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow><mn>0</mn></mfenced></math>, <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 1 comma 0 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mn>1</mn><mn>0</mn></mfenced></math>, and <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 4 comma 0 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mn>4</mn><mn>0</mn></mfenced></math>. Which of the following must be a factor of <math alttext=\"f left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
